{{define "subject"}}{{if eq (len .Bookmarks) 1}}1 application deadline in 3 days{{else}}{{len .Bookmarks}} application deadlines in 3 days{{end}}{{end}}

{{define "plainBody"}}
Hi {{.FirstName}},

A heads-up — you have {{len .Bookmarks}} {{if eq (len .Bookmarks) 1}}application deadline{{else}}application deadlines{{end}} in your shortlist closing in 3 days.

{{range .Bookmarks}}
- {{.Title}} — {{.EmployerName}}
  Deadline: {{.Deadline.Format "Mon, 02 Jan 2006"}}
  View: {{$.FrontendURL}}/opportunities/{{.OpportunitySlug}}

{{end}}

Don't let these pass — head to your shortlist when you have a moment:
{{.FrontendURL}}/shortlist

— The GradConnect Team
{{end}}

{{define "htmlBody"}}
<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
